      "writtenOn": "2026-07-03T16:57:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "```suggestion\n[Android Developer Verification](https://developer.android.com/developer-verification) is Google\u0027s requirement, rolling out regionally starting September 2026 (global by 2027), that apps be registered to an identity-verified developer before they can be installed on a \"certified\" Android device — that is, any device shipping Google Play, Play Services, and the rest of the Google Mobile Services (GMS) suite. This applies regardless of the installation source; whether it is the Play Store, third-party stores, or direct APK sideload.\n\n```",
