      "message": "```suggestion\nThis is a different situation from [Play Integrity](https://wiki.lineageos.org/quirks/snet/): Play Integrity\u0027s attestation logic lives inside Play Services itself, and apps call into it directly for attestation. Developer Verification, by contrast, is its own standalone app that the frameworks are pointed at as a provider.\n```",
