      "writtenOn": "2026-07-03T16:57:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "```suggestion\nIf you sideload [GApps packages](https://wiki.lineageos.org/glossary/#gapps), be aware that a GApps package could choose to bundle \"AndroidDeveloperVerification\" and enable it. We\u0027re not aware of any reason an aftermarket GApps package would opt into that, since doing so would restrict what its own users can sideload. If your GApps provider ever does, you can simply switch to a different package.\n```",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 39,
        "startChar": 16,
        "endLine": 39,
        "endChar": 30
      },
